videoframe.name: videoframe
videoframe.description: Enterprise name space assigned to Videoframe Systems by IANA.

vfGeneric.name: vfGeneric
vfGeneric.description: Name space for object definitions common among Videoframe managed devices.

vfProducts.name: vfProducts
vfProducts.description: Name space for object definitions specific to particular Videoframe managed device types.

vfExperimental.name: vfExperimental
vfExperimental.description: vfExperimental provides a root OID from which experimental MIBs are temporarily based. MIBs that are placed here are Videoframe works-in-progress and have not been assigned a permanent OID by Videoframe, typically because the MIB was not ready for deployment.

vfRegistrations.name: vfRegistrations
vfRegistrations.description: Name space for Videoframe's authoritatively assigned registrations and MIB modules.

vfMIBModules.name: vfMIBModules
vfMIBModules.description: Name space for Registration of MIB modules defined by videoframe systems.
